
Start tmux          tmux

Create new window   ^b c
End current window  ^b & (and ~ end)
Next window         ^b n
Previous window     ^b p
List windows        ^b w
Split pane vert     ^b %
Split pane horiz    ^b "
Move between panes  ^b [arrow keys]
Detach session      ^b d
Reattach later      tmux attach

